data.name: enterTeamName.Text
data.value:
Hello, welcome to the five-a-side dream league simulator. To get started you will need to input your team.
-The team willl consist of a captain, four regular players and one substitute -You will be given a number of skill points for each player to allocate to attributes that determine what kind of player they are -The captain will be given more total skill points to allocate, and the substitute will have a lower number -You can allocate the skill points for each player on their respective tabs, but first you need to enter your team name on this page
Choose wisely!
